Comment.val: /*Function to calculate de positionValue based on historic positionData. Startdate is only used to create a list of dates. Start of history date is recomended.*/

SQL_STMT_U.val: select instrument_id, position, quot_midden quote from ( -- position on date selection select * from -- date selection (select to_date(~1, 'YYYYMMDD') + (level - 1) as test_date from dual where to_date(~1, 'YYYYMMDD') + (level - 1) between to_date(~1, 'YYYYMMDD') and sysdate connect by level <= (300*366)) d -- position selection , (select b.calc_date position_date , lead(b.calc_date-1, 1, sysdate) over ( partition by b.pere_id, p.instrument_id order by b.pere_id, p.instrument_id, b.calc_date) as next_position_date , b.pere_id , p.instrument_id , p.position from pc_historic_portfolio_position p inner join pc_historic_portfolio_base b on b.id = p.phpb_id where b.pere_id = ~3) p where d.test_date between p.position_date and p.next_position_date and d.test_date = to_date(~2,'YYYYMMDD')) pd , (--quotes on date selection select * from -- date selection (select to_date(~1, 'YYYYMMDD') + (level - 1) as test_date from dual where to_date(~1, 'YYYYMMDD') + (level - 1) between to_date(~1, 'YYYYMMDD') and sysdate connect by level <= (300*366)) d -- quote selection , (select to_date(f.quot_datum, 'YYYYMMDD') quote_date, lead(to_date(f.quot_datum,'YYYYMMDD')-1, 1, sysdate) over ( partition by b.be_volgnummer order by b.be_volgnummer, f.quot_soort, f.quot_datum, f.quot_tijd) as next_quote_date , f.quot_midden, b.be_volgnummer from fn_quotes_vw f inner join beleggingsinstrument b on b.be_symbool = f.quot_symbool and b.be_optietype = f.quot_optietype and b.be_expiratiedatum = f.quot_expiratiedatum and b.be_exerciseprijs = f.quot_exerciseprijs and (b.be_volgnummer in (select distinct p.instrument_id from pc_historic_portfolio_position p inner join pc_historic_portfolio_base b on b.id = p.phpb_id where (b.pere_id = ~3) and f.quot_soort = 'SLOT') )) q where d.test_date between q.quote_date and q.next_quote_date and d.test_date = to_date(~2,'YYYYMMDD')) qd where pd.instrument_id = qd.be_volgnummer
